---
const faqs = [
  {
    q: 'Why is Download disabled in Teams?',
    a: 'Tenant admins turn it off org-wide; meeting organisers can also toggle it per meeting. The recording itself isn\'t locked — just the convenience button is hidden.',
  },
  {
    q: 'Does this bypass access restrictions?',
    a: 'No. It runs as you, against your own session. If you can\'t play it natively, you can\'t download it.',
  },
  {
    q: 'Will it work on DRM-protected recordings?',
    a: 'No, and no tool does. Widevine/PlayReady decrypt only inside the browser\'s DRM module. The extension detects it and shows a clear dialog.',
  },
  {
    q: 'Can I generate MP3 or WAV?',
    a: 'Not anymore. Microsoft now AES-128-CBC encrypts SharePoint Stream segments and no CLI tool (ffmpeg, yt-dlp, etc.) can handle the fragments. Download MP4 or M4A in-browser, then transcode locally if you need a different format.',
  },
  {
    q: 'How fast is the in-browser download?',
    a: 'Segments fetch in parallel (default 4, tunable up to 16) over a single HTTP/2 connection. Multi-track mux runs on a Web Worker so the UI never freezes. 429s are auto-retried with exponential backoff — transient throttling won\'t fail the download.',
  },
  {
    q: 'Is anything sent to a third-party server?',
    a: 'No. Zero telemetry. The extension talks to Microsoft URLs and nothing else.',
  },
  {
    q: 'What about Firefox?',
    a: 'Chrome and Edge only for now. Firefox port is on the longer-term list.',
  },
  {
    q: 'What if the meeting was never transcribed?',
    a: 'The transcript button shows a clear "no transcript available" dialog. No silent failure.',
  },
  {
    q: 'Is it free?',
    a: 'Yes. MIT-licensed, open source, no premium tier, no upsell.',
  },
  {
    q: 'How do I uninstall?',
    a: 'chrome://extensions → Remove. The only stored data is your last-used transcript format, wiped on uninstall.',
  },
];
---
<section id="faq" class="hairline">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-[1280px] px-6 lg:px-10 py-20 lg:py-28">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-10 mb-14">
      <div class="lg:col-span-4">
        <p class="section-num">06 / faq</p>
      </div>
      <div class="lg:col-span-8">
        <div class="border border-border">
          {faqs.map((f, i) => (
            <details class="group border-b last:border-b-0 border-border" open={i === 0}>
              <summary class="cursor-pointer px-6 py-5 flex items-start gap-5 text-fg list-none hover:bg-bg-elev transition-colors">
                <span class="section-num shrink-0 mt-1">{String(i + 1).padStart(2, '0')}</span>
                <span class="flex-1 text-[14px] leading-[1.5]">{f.q}</span>
                <span class="text-red shrink-0 mt-1 group-open:rotate-45 transition-transform inline-block">+</span>
              </summary>
              <div class="px-6 pb-5 pl-[3.875rem] text-[13px] text-fg-dim leading-[1.7] -mt-1">
                {f.a}
              </div>
            </details>
          ))}
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
